    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Raptors/status/2034264196108427527",
      "reply_text": "Raptors on the road, tough one tonight",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:08:21.291294+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBACobwebs/status/2034263936334491964",
      "reply_text": "Impressive shooting night from Bird. 34 in the first half, though?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:09:06.489879+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Keith_Langlois/status/2034259925887549809",
      "reply_text": "Tough break for Cade. Hope he's back soon.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:09:37.803739+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FantasyBall365/status/2034258972832600266",
      "reply_text": "Giannis out indefinitely opens up a lot of minutes for him. Still a solid ROS option",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:10:32.498977+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheNBABase/status/2034259451323252908",
      "reply_text": "That's a significant regression. Defense matters in the playoffs.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:11:23.322204+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TommyBeer/status/2034266585515380841",
      "reply_text": "That's some crazy efficiency",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:22:36.852203+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheWestWolfPod/status/2034264978132205612",
      "reply_text": "Westbrook's lead is massive. He's been a scoring force his whole career.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:23:28.551754+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/alexscnovaes/status/2034267409675071958",
      "reply_text": "Celtics and Warriors are a tough matchup. Should be a good one.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:23:59.061913+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheWestWolfPod/status/2034265700055814593",
      "reply_text": "Westbrook's lead is massive",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:24:46.344521+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/detxspartan/status/2034261278860988747",
      "reply_text": "That's not the reason he left. Not sure what's going on with his role this year though.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:25:25.998523+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TurnAndBurn210/status/2034254686459437289",
      "reply_text": "That's awesome, family rivalries make it even sweeter when you stick with your team.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:26:04.128000+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Filmdaddy77/status/2034238038923210816",
      "reply_text": "Not sure that's the whole story, though. He's had his own share of injuries in the league too.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:26:53.659051+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JoeDellera/status/2034266031208697863",
      "reply_text": "Luka's been unstoppable. What's the over/under on his assists too?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:36:52.643216+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LukaDoncicStanD/status/2034272224014721315",
      "reply_text": "Not sure what's more surprising, the MVP talk or the disrespect towards Cade and JB's seasons.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:37:30.086930+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BConn63/status/2034264422344995179",
      "reply_text": "Congrats to Elian and Tom. Well-deserved recognition",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-18T14:38:09.384785+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BetBettorSports/status/2034268317687443960",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, he's been rebounding a lot. That's a good bet.",
